{
  "stem": "1029.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a short walk to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody was watching us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was embarrassing because people were watching us, people who knew us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we arrived, they assigned us rooms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a big meeting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They pulled us all into this middle of this big opening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the gendarme, the rendorseg, as it was called in Hungarian, they told us how to behave, not to escape because if we did anything like that, we would be shot.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was the first time I heard that our lives-- we were going to be shot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sounded like a, a comic tale, like a something you see in a movie, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You saw people being shot in movie.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew that it was make-believe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But actually, we were going to be shot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I could feel my mother you know, stiffening you know, when she heard this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she started crying and the tears.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and I was concerned, I must say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of the-- well, well, we couldn't leave the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We needed permission to see a doctor or to see a dentist.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anybody caught outside the ghetto was supposed to be shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But nobody was shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, it was a little village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just didn't try to leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There may have been some escapees.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I heard something, but, but I don't remember if anybody wanted to escape.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We heard stories that they are going to take us to, to a place where we're going to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We're going to be in a work detail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were going to get paid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We're going to be like a displaced workforce.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then after the war, we are going to be brought back.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
